cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on using deep learning models for image recognition of cassava diseases, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of transfer learning and convolutional neural networks also suggests the paper could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of mobile devices for disease detection, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves accessing and analyzing large amounts of data.
